DENGUE/DHF UPDATE 2004 (17)
***************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.promedmail.org>
ProMED-mail is a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
<http://www.isid.org>
[This is by no means a comprehensive collection of all reports of dengue in
the world since the last update. We try to focus on places where there is a
significant increase in cases, or which have DHF & deaths. In order to make
our updates more inclusive, ProMED-mail asks readers to send reports of
dengue outbreaks that they find to <promed@promedmail.org>.]

In this update:
[1] USA (Texas)
[2] Sri Lanka
[3] & [4] Saudi Arabia (Jeddah)
